      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e7f32ee0727ca078e7fb63e?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1191&rangeEnd=1259"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41721976_44_42523-42582",
      "chapterUid": 44,
      "range": "42523-42582",
      "markText": "他没有唱完。又一颗子弹，还是同一个枪手射来的，戛然打断他的歌声。这次他脸朝地倒下，不再动弹了。这孩子的伟大灵魂飞升了。",
      "totalCount": 432,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41721976&chapterUid=44&rangeStart=42523&rangeEnd=42582",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e7f32ee0727ca078e7fb63e?chapterUid=44&rangeStart=42523&rangeEnd=42582"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41721976_6_44158-44226",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "44158-44226",
      "markText": "“冉阿让，我的兄弟，您不再属于恶的一方，而属于善的一方了。我买下了您的灵魂；我把您的灵魂从邪恶的念头和沉沦的思想中赎出来，交给上帝了。”",
      "totalCount": 420,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41721976&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=44158&rangeEnd=44226",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e7f32ee0727ca078e7fb63e?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=44158&rangeEnd=44226"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41721976_8_8077-8100",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "8077-8100",
      "markText": "人们总是从容地安排启程，殊不知往往是生离死别。",
